puakma.util
Class URLReader

java.lang.Object
  puakma.util.URLReader
public class URLReader
extends java.lang.Object

This class is used to get or post HTTP data to/from a remote server. URLReader ur = new URLReader("http://yourserver/yourapp.pma"); byte bufReply[] = sc.send(null, false); By default messages will not be compressed with gzip. Session ID, username/password and Ltpa token info may be set
